    "It mainly consists of four steps.",
    "Sentence Splitting.",
    "MultiUN (Eisele and Chen, 2010) performs sentence segmentation on extracted text.",
    "Chinese text is segmented using a simple regular expression, while other texts use the sentence tokenization module from the NLTK toolkit 26.",
    "Corpus2020 (Xu et al, 2020c) utilizes PyLTP (Python Language Technology Platform) to separate text into complete sentences, with one sentence per line."
